This repo reproduces an issue when using toolchains_llvm 1.6.0 with a remote_cache

````
bazel build ...
bazel shutdown
bazel build ...
````

Bazel rebuilds all targets.

Now, if you remove this line from the .bazelrc:

````
build --remote_cache=http://127.0.0.1:404
````

Doing the above will not result in a rebuild. All targets are foud in thea action cache.
